inspiracio.net
Class IHttpURLConnection

java.lang.Object
  java.net.URLConnection
      java.net.HttpURLConnection
          inspiracio.net.IHttpURLConnection

public final class IHttpURLConnection
extends HttpURLConnection

A wrapper for HttpURLConnection that can do gzip.

Now, it does gzip always. It would be better to negotiate with the server.
